DERIVA Client Tools is a application software bundle for working with the DERIVA platform (deriva.isi.edu).

It contains both GUI applications and command-line applications.

The DERIVA Authentication Agent is a GUI application which authenticates to DERIVA services and runs in the background,
providing authentication services to other locally installed client applications.

The DERIVA Upload Utility is a GUI application that provides batch upload of data and file assets to DERIVA servers.

DERIVA Command Line Applications opens a Terminal shell environment from which the various DERIVA CLI tools can be launched.